Master Gadrin
Get enough gold to buy the dungeon key and go inside it to kill Ragnarog.
This is it, #. <Gadrin points to the vial inside the bag.> The blood of innocents. The purest blood. It is with this blood that Kirtonos may be summoned. It is with this blood, then, that Kirtonos must be destroyed. Take the dungeon key and go inside the dungeon. Ragnarog will come - he cannot resist. When he appears, unleash the fury and wrath of a thousand innocent deaths upon him. Should you succeed, you will earn more than just our gratitude.
